body:
Additional information - the latest commit - top of tree:
git log

```
commit b3d10f43833f065ec0e635ce6cdb2332f4ee5049
Merge: a39be7c ea7b20d
Author: bors <bors@rust-lang.org>
Date:   Tue Jan 28 05:11:28 2014 -0800
...
```

Found commit related to LLVM:

```
commit ea7b20d8f279ea8c63b9a4b8e9129fce0e3c2b5d
Author: comex <comexk@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Jan 28 00:05:33 2014 -0500

    Add appropriate LLVM module flags for debug info.

    Set "Dwarf Version" to 2 on OS X to avoid toolchain incompatibility, and
    set "Debug Info Version" to prevent debug info from being stripped from
    bitcode.

    Fixes #11352.
```

Thanks
Can you provide a paste of the full session? The `rustllvm` library should have be automatically rebuilt...
